!! ### Error (non-standard language) tags

+Err/Orth         !!≈ * **@CODE@** substandard form
+Err/Lex          !!≈ * **@CODE@** substandard word
+Err/DerSub       !!≈ * **@CODE@** substandard for derivation
+Err/CmpSub       !!≈ * **@CODE@** substandard for compounding
+Err/MissingSpace !!≈ * **@CODE@** missing a space
+Err/MissingHyph  !!≈ * **@CODE@** missing a hyphen
+Err/Hyph         !!≈ * **@CODE@** unnecessary extra hyphen
+Err/SpaceCmp     !!≈ * **@CODE@** extra space in compound
+Err/Spellrelax   !!≈ * **@CODE@** typos under spell relax
+Err/Confused      !!≈ * **@CODE@** confusion pairs

!! ## Usage tags

+Use/-Spell       !!≈ * **@CODE@** excluded from speller
+Use/SpellNoSugg  !!≈ * **@CODE@** recognized but not suggested in speller
+Use/Circ         !!≈ * **@CODE@** circular paths
+Use/NG           !!≈ * **@CODE@** excluded from generators
+Use/PMatch       !!≈ * **@CODE@** included in tokenisers only
+Use/-PMatch      !!≈ * **@CODE@** excluded from tokeisers
+Use/GC           !!≈ * **@CODE@** included in grammar checker only
+Use/-GC          !!≈ * **@CODE@** excluded from grammar checker
+Use/TTS          !!≈ * **@CODE@** included in text-to-speech only
+Use/-TTS         !!≈ * **@CODE@** excluded from text-to-speech

! ### Dialect tags:

+Dial/-XYZ  !!≈ * **@CODE@** forms not in use in
+Dial/XYZ  !!≈ * **@CODE@** forms in use in

!! ## Tags for indicating the orthography used
+Orth/Strd !!≈ @CODE@ - Standard orthography
+Orth/IPA  !!≈ @CODE@ - IPA transcription

!! ## Tags for indicating alternative orthographies, cf `configure.ac`
+AltOrth/standard  !!≈ @CODE@ - Standard orthography
+AltOrth/-standard !!≈ @CODE@ - NOT Standard orthography



