LEXICON Root
!! The word forms in Gunwinggu language start from the lexeme roots of basic
!! word classes, or optionally from prefixes:

functionwords ;

@P.TYPE.V@ TSOPreBase ;
AllNounClasses ;
NounGenderPreBase ;
NominalPrefixes ;
AdjBase ;
AdvBase ;
Punctuation ;
Symbols ;


